  <entry>
    <title>Sleep position</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2018/05/18/pillow/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2018/05/18/pillow/</id>
    <published>2018-05-18T04:23:46.717Z</published>
    <updated>2018-05-30T01:52:17.909Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><font color="#FFA500" size="14">The name of the game is spinal alignment.<br></font><blockquote><p>one 参考<a href="https://sleepsherpa.com/proper-pillow-height-determines-best-pillow/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Link</a><br>the height of pillow AND your sleep position<br>侧卧者可以在他们的腿之间放置一个枕头以缓冲并防止脊柱扭转。<br>How you sleep during the night and feel in the morning is the true test of whether or not a pillow is right for you. You should give it at least a week to make a conclusion. 可以一点一点地加高。</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>two 参考<a href="https://jysk.co.uk/guide/pillow-guide" target="_blank" rel="noopener">link</a><br><img src="art01.jpg" alt="avatar"><br><a href="https://www.spine-health.com/wellness/sleep/pillow-support-and-comfort" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.spine-health.com/wellness/sleep/pillow-support-and-comfort</a></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>便宜啊<a href="https://www.ikea.com/us/en/catalog/categories/departments/bedroom/20533/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.ikea.com/us/en/catalog/categories/departments/bedroom/20533/</a><br><a href="https://www.quora.com/What-is-the-right-pillow-height" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.quora.com/What-is-the-right-pillow-height</a></p></blockquote><p>完美的枕头支撑你的脖子，使颈椎尽可能地躺在你的脊柱上。尽管你可能会喜欢它，但你现在的枕头做到这一点还远远没有确定。习惯的力量是引人注目的，所以你可能已经习惯了用厚厚的羽毛枕头睡觉，即使它不能为你的身体提供最好的支持。将自己从一种特定类型的枕头中取出可能很难。如果作为一种过渡措施，甚至在将来，您可以睡两个枕头，这可以在夜间切换，这可能会有所帮助。<br>如果你睡在你身边，你应该有一个相对较高的枕头，它填满了你的脸颊和床垫之间的整个肩部。另一方面，如果你喜欢睡在你的背上，你的枕头应该很低，并且主要支撑你的脖子。泡沫或天然乳胶中的特殊人体工程学枕头非常适用于此目的。脖子下的额外支撑确保了最佳的支持。</p>]]></content>
    
